                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18310908-331-off1701 t18310908-331-cd1702"></join>, 1 frock, value 1s. 6d.; 1 waistcoat, value 3d.; 1 jacket, value 3d.; 2 pairs of trousers, value 1s.; 5 yards of plaid, value 2s.; 1 handkerchief, value 1s. 6d., and 1 hair front, value 3d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               
